E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Nhu%E1%BA%ADn/T%E1%BB%A5ng-gi%C3%A1-t%C3%A2y-chinh-ph%E1%BB%A5ng-ho%E1%BA%A1-ng%E1%BB%B1-ch%E1%BA%BF-T%C6%B0-gia-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-s%C4%A9/poem-l79rHQkavhwnGh_ZBVIn_A">Tụng giá tây chinh phụng hoạ ngự chế “Tư gia tướng sĩ” - 從駕西征奉和御製思家將士</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Nhu%E1%BA%ADn/author-M-50xx2ow4YFv2TP3AmR1w">Đỗ Nhuận</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BA%BFt-%C4%90%C3%A0o/V%E1%BB%8Dng-xu%C3%A2n-t%E1%BB%AB-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-a4-LIwzBkXIkbL9zTRP2bA">Vọng xuân từ kỳ 2 - 春望詞其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BA%BFt-%C4%90%C3%A0o/author-YFc6G7OeOIRiUPVl88lFdA">Tiết Đào</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Y%E1%BA%BFt-H%E1%BB%81-T%C6%B0/V%C5%A9-thu%E1%BA%ADt-tam-thi%C3%AAn-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-T6z1-FRywBFCAaxAOBr3bg">Vũ thuật tam thiên kỳ 3 - 雨述三篇其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Y%E1%BA%BFt-H%E1%BB%81-T%C6%B0/author-iORDIpdUm3k9JfYMnUFi-Q">Yết Hề Tư</a>)<br></div>	</div>
